{"lemma":"رَيْعٌ","slug":"رَيْعٌ","root":"ر.#.ع","root_slug":"ر-_-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-_-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"رَيْعٌ","root":"ريع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n17261"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92%D8%B9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n17261","headword_ar":"رَيْعٌ","root":"ryE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[see 1, of which it is an inf. n.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Increase;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ziyaAdapN","text_ar":"زِيَادَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which may be meant to include the third of the significations here following]; as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA TaEaAmN kaviyru Alr~ayoEi","text_ar":"هٰذَا طَعَامٌ كَثِيرُ الرَّيْعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is wheat of much increase"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh.) ―         -b2-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Revenue arising from the increase of land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"because it is an augmentation. (Mgh.) ―         -b3-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Milk;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqapN kaviyrapN rayoEuhaA","text_ar":"نَاقَةٌ كَثِيرَةٌ رَيْعُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A she-camel whose milk is abundant"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Redundance; a part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion, redundant; a surplus;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a residue;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faDolN","text_ar":"فَضْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; of anything; as of flour, or meal, (Msb, K,) over and above the measure of the wheat; (Msb;) and of dough [when it has risen]; and of seed for sowing [when it has been sown]; and the like. (K.) Hence it is said, in a trad. of I'Ab, respecting the expiation of an oath,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"likul~i","text_ar":"لِكُلِّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misokiynK mud~N mino HinoTapK rayoEuhu A_idaAmuhu","text_ar":"مِسْكِينٍ مُدٌّ مِنْ حِنْطَةٍ رَيْعُهُ اـِدَامُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"To every poor man, a mudd of wheat: the redundance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"redundant part"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion, thereof"},{"kind":"text","text":"shall be for"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its seasoning"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: i. e., it is not necessary for the person to give, with the mudd, seasoning; but the redundance that shall arise, of the flour, or meal, of the mudd [of wheat], when he shall have ground it, therewith shall the seasoning be bought. (TA.) Hence also, the trad. of 'Omar,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AimolikuwA","text_ar":"اِمْلِكُوا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEajiyna faA_in~ahu A^aHadu Alr~ayoEayoni","text_ar":"العَجِينَ فَاـِنَّهُ اَحَدُ الرَّيْعَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Knead ye well,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thoroughly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soundly, the dough; for this"},{"kind":"text","text":"action"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is one of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayoEaAni","text_ar":"رَيْعَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two causes of redundance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the other cause being the grinding]. (TA.) [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayoEu Ald~iroEi","text_ar":"رَيْعُ الدِّرْعِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The redundant parts of the two sleeves of the coat of mail,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"over"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and beyond"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the ends of the fingers;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and of the skirt thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b5-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyEN","text_ar":"رِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b6-  Also, (K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayoEaAnN","text_ar":"رَيْعَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [which latter is the more common in this sense,] (S, K,) (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and most excel-lent"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything: (S, K:) said in the B to be a metaphorical application from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayoEN","text_ar":"رَيْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a high,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an elevated, place."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) Hence, (S, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayoEu Al$~abaAbi","text_ar":"رَيْعُ الشَّبَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", by poetic license written ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayaE","text_ar":"رَيَع","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~abaAbi","text_ar":"الشَّبَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayoEaAnu","text_ar":"رَيْعَانُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, L, TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The first,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prime,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and most excellent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"period, of youth"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"youthfulness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"youthful vigour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, TA:) or this is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayoEN","text_ar":"رَيْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in relation to wheat: (A, TA:) or from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaTari","text_ar":"المَطَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayoEaAnu","text_ar":"رَيْعَانُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the first of rain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA.) Hence also, (S,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~araAbi","text_ar":"السَّرَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayoEaAnu","text_ar":"رَيْعَانُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Sgh, L) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The first of the mirage;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Sgh;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what comes and goes thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sgh;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is in a state of commotion"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agitation, quivering, vibrating,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moving to and fro."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayoEu AlD~uHaY","text_ar":"رَيْعُ الضُّحَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The whiteness, and beautiful splendour, of the first part of the day after sunrise."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqapN lahaA rayoEN","text_ar":"نَاقَةٌ لَهَا رَيْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A she-camel having one pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rate of going,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a quicker pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN layosa lahu rayoEN","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ لَيْسَ لَهُ رَيْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marojuwEN","text_ar":"مَرْجُوعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one has no reply,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"answer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"to give: or, perhaps,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to such a one there is no reply,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"answer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"to be given]. (K, * TA.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fright,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fear;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoEN","text_ar":"رَوْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","S","A","TA","L","Sgh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}